---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: "Mortgage Recast vs Remortgage in the UK (2026 Guide)",
  description: "Comprehensive guide to UK mortgage overpayments, 10% annual allowance limits, Early Repayment Charges (ERCs), and remortgaging strategies.",
  schema: `
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Article",
        "headline": "Mortgage Recast vs Remortgage in the UK",
        "author": {
          "@type": "Person",
          "name": "Mrittunjoy Das"
        },
        "publisher": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": "TaxDebtWealthSuite"
        },
        "datePublished": "2026-07-23",
        "dateModified": "2026-07-23",
        "description": "Comprehensive guide to UK mortgage overpayments, 10% annual allowance limits, Early Repayment Charges (ERCs), and remortgaging strategies."
      }
    </script>
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Does the UK have mortgage recasting?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Formal 'recasting' is rare in the UK. UK borrowers usually make overpayments (typically up to 10% annually without Early Repayment Charges) or adjust terms during remortgaging."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    </script>
  `
};
---

<Layout title={seo.title} description={seo.description} head={seo.schema}>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest border border-emerald-500/20 mb-6">
        <span>UK Real Estate & Debt</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
        Mortgage Recast vs Remortgage in the UK
      </h1>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Mrittunjoy+Das&background=00F5D4&color=000" alt="Mrittunjoy Das" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full" />
          By <span class="text-white font-medium">Mrittunjoy Das</span>
        </span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time datetime="2026-07-23">July 23, 2026</time>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Embedded Calculator Callout Banner -->
    <div class="my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#141C32] to-[#1E294B] border border-[#00F5D4]/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-1">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#00F5D4] uppercase tracking-wider">Interactive Tool</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">UK Mortgage Overpayment Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">Calculate UK overpayments and monthly payment reductions.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/mortgage-recast-calculator/uk/" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[#00F5D4] hover:bg-[#00F5D4]/90 text-slate-950 font-bold text-xs whitespace-nowrap transition-all shadow-lg shadow-[#00F5D4]/20">
        Calculate UK Overpayment →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Homeowners in the United Kingdom looking to lower monthly mortgage costs often hear about American "mortgage recasting" and wonder if similar options exist under UK banking rules. While formal recasting is rare in the UK market, UK mortgage borrowers have access to powerful overpayment mechanics, flexi-mortgage features, and remortgaging options regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">1. The UK 10% Overpayment Rule</h2>
      <p>
        Most UK lenders permit up to 10% penalty-free annual overpayments. Borrowers can request a monthly payment recalculation to lower their monthly check.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">Related Calculators & Strategy Guides</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
        <a href="/mortgage-recast-calculator/uk/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#00F5D4]/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#00F5D4] uppercase">Calculator</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">UK Overpayment Tool</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Calculate UK overpayments & monthly savings.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/debt-payoff-calculator/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400 uppercase">Related Tool</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Debt Payoff Planner</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Evaluate debt snowball vs avalanche payoff methods.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/buy-borrow-die-calculator/uk/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-amber-500/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase">Related Tool</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Buy, Borrow, Die Calculator</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Model asset liquidity vs property equity accumulation.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
